Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.40,0:00:03.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们继续去找鹰之团了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:18.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.40,0:00:36.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,光之鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.67,0:00:40.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 为什么敢来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.68,0:00:45.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.72,0:01:00.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.54,0:01:04.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在干什么 还不杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:06.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,放箭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.75,0:01:07.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:15.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,箭一支都没
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:19.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然躲开了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:20.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那么多的数量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:27.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢货 发什么呆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.65,0:01:28.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,第二波 放箭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:32.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么东西
Comment: 0,0:03:08.28,0:03:10.37,DefaultSub,,0,0,0,,/-------START------/
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:13.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个男人的同伙吗 把这家伙干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:22.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个剑士怎么回事 是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:25.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,坚持住敌人 只有两人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:27.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快点捉住他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:40.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 敌阵前不能下马
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:46.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫劳古斯 按照神谕的指引来此参战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.29,0:03:50.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,想必你就是光之鹰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:54.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,月光骑士劳古斯 你的剑我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:55.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,敬心喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.11,0:03:58.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,光之鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:03:59.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,鹰?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:00.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:02.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,听说已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:07.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我在温达姆城凯旋避行中见过 肯定是他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:12.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那位大人才是米特兰的守护神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:18.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:22.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:23.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:25.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你等等 危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:26.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格里菲斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:30.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,风在耳语着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:34.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,现在世界要阔始改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:40.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止他们 阻止那两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:41.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:42.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:45.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,顾及这些家伙的生死有什么好处
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:49.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,先趁着混乱 把鹰抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.23,0:04:56.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,世上竟有如此美丽的人 美得不像人类一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:02.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:11.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 竟然把我们击飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:14.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真慢 迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:20.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,作为巴基拉卡的顶尖的达巴沙叫人失望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:23.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这个面具 你是拉克沙斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:26.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,族中的流放者为何在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:31.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我听预言说 你就是光之鹰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:35.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你真美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:41.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天 我要割下你的头颅 让它属于我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.87,0:05:51.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前我不会让别人伤害你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:54.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,陪你们俩玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:08.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,关上城门 断绝他们的退路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.78,0:06:17.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,巨人 龙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:20.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,别退缩 敌人只有一个上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:38.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,传令 要塞里的人全部出击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:41.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:43.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.65,0:07:00.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,扑鼻的味道 弥漫着的血腥味让脑袋里都麻木了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:03.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,全都染红了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:11.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,夕阳的照射下 全都一片血红
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:14.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如此惨绝人寰的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.79,0:07:22.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 但那是世上绝无仅有的一幅图画
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:31.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在确确实实就在这骇人听闻的故事当中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:52.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,请您让我们加入您的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:55.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你还不快跪下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:58.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:01.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,太可疑了 突然改变态度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:04.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是想钻空子抓我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:08.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经舍弃教籍还俗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:11.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能相信你们这帮贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:17.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道 超越了我所深信的秩序的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:22.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我想学习 能在没有秩序的黑暗中生存的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:25.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,从你那里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:32.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,请指引我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:39.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,想用难懂的话蒙混过去可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:44.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你们对卡思嘉大姐做的事该怎解决
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:50.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,差点就被火烧了要想让昨日的敌人变成朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.51,0:08:55.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,来给大爷跪一下吧 做得到吗 自傲的贵族们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:59.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,想打吗 来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:09.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只能做这些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:12.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,早晚有一天会谢罪的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:19.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你要再得寸进尺的话就是真正的反派了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:23.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,少爷和贵族小姐都那么夸张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:25.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,随你们的便
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:27.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那么说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:29.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 好干脆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:32.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,交代和道歉都不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:35.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我也干掉了你们的同伴 彼此彼此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:40.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是指引就算了 我不适合那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:43.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你想知道什么随便做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:47.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不碍我的事 我也不会说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:48.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:50.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,说这个还早
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:55.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和我们一起走 就意味着能睡觉的夜晚不会再来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:59.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,还会有幽灵 怪物出现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:01.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,求之不得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:07.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有点奇怪 那个格斯竟然这么会干脆的接受别人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:17.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个人的话 以前的我一定会不由分说拒绝的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:21.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话这次真是难办了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:26.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我竟然第一次这么期待别人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.28,0:10:31.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为自己的不详而战傈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:36.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被自己的无力所打垮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:45.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,她最后一次欢笑是什么时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.10,0:11:03.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不是对王室尽忠也不是为了贵族的脸面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:04.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,而是为了拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:06.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的领民们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:09.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:12.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,跟着我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:18.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是 米特兰人的俘虏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:23.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵 全军齐射 放箭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.90,0:11:28.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,连自己人也
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:30.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,用箭瞄准吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:33.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,骑兵突击 全歼他们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:36.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.37,0:11:39.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:54.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是援军
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:57.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,右翼有新敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:05.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,左翼也有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:12.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他们到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:23.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:25.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个旗帜是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:41.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:45.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一道白光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:49.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,直指敌人意志的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:54.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格里菲斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:00.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,飞 飞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:39.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:42.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这里真的是战场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:43.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这么祥和的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:47.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到是被异国军队蹂躏的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:49.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是格里菲斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:52.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格里菲斯是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:54.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那位白鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.48,0:13:55.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为有格里菲斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:57.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们才能露出笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:00.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这位少女是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:02.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,难道读了我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:06.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到鹰之团
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:14.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,士气多么高涨的士兵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:17.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,库夏人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:19.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是库夏人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:20.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:21.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,还说是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:23.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:24.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么敌人在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:26.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,问题一个一个问啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:27.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是顺从者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:30.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:32.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这异样的压迫感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:35.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我军的规定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:39.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,俘虏要三次上场冲锋之后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:42.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,活下来的可以选择归降或者自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:45.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,顺从者们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:49.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,根据之后的表现可以和普通士兵一样得到晋升机会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.11,0:14:52.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,根据情况还能领兵打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:54.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这太胡来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:56.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把士兵托付给敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:59.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,库夏人也不是一块磐石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:05.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是一个王族打败不同的部族后才获得帝位的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.51,0:15:08.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这里面有很多深仇大恨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:10.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:13.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们米特兰人的感受怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:17.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,街道 家庭 父母兄弟被杀的人的怨恨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:23.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说各有怨恨但大家都是人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:25.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这要待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:29.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就能明白往日的敌人更容易变得亲近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.66,0:15:32.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个骑士是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:34.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是劳古斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:37.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,负责鹰之团的新兵训练
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:38.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,劳古斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:40.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是那个月光骑士劳古斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:43.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,果然吓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:45.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,习武之人都这一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:48.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在无数战场上立下武勋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.72,0:15:51.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,御前比武和决斗没有败绩的荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:55.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不跟从一位主人 游历至今的最强骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:58.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那位活生生的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:01.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:06.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你还会更加吃惊的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.33,0:16:11.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,比劳古斯大人说的库夏人还要吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.16,0:16:13.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这边是近路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:21.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什么在这个森林里盘踞着的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.17,0:16:23.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,异常的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:27.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,野兽 还是狼群吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:29.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:39.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没注意到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:42.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,也在白天的战斗中大显身手了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:44.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家称之为战魔兵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:46.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,战魔兵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:53.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这样还算好很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:56.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,以前还吃过库夏人的俘虏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:01.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,小 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:04.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你又一个人来这里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:07.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,别闹了赶紧放我下来 色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:12.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好就没吃过人类的肉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:15.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我要和格里菲斯大人去告状
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:17.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这个千万不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:25.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,古伦贝路多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:34.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人是我们主人的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:37.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要出手的话我来做你对手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.42,0:17:39.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑的 只是开个玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:40.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,古伦贝路多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:42.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:44.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,从大国莸塔的进攻中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:48.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在北方小国仅凭自己率领的三千兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:52.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,坚守十年的巨人豪杰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:54.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,火之巨龙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:57.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说他应该战死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:18:00.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,索妮亚 你也太不小心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.06,0:18:02.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是鹰的巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:05.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能一个人不带就来这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:09.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,下次要来的时候和我打声招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:11.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:14.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,鹰之巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:18.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他们到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:22.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不太清楚详情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:25.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,莫名其妙的非人军团
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.09,0:18:28.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,名震世界的英雄们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:29.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这里到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:38.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我带格里菲斯大人的客人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:47.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:51.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,今天死在战场上的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:54.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗结束之后会变成幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:56.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样聚集起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:00.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,死者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:01.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:04.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:10.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:13.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,战死者的血亲或者恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:15.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,来进行最后道别的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:17.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:24.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:25.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:30.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.65,0:19:32.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:49.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:52.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格里菲斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:55.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,白天辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:56.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,索妮亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:19:58.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不算什么大事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:20:03.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和格里菲斯大人在一起我的力量也变强了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:07.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这个男人就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.77,0:20:08.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,白色的鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:14.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那群光到底要去向何处
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:18.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,成为一体之处
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:20.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,成为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:22.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:24.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,天国 还是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:26.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你总有一天会明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:28.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人都会有那么一天的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:32.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,很荣幸见到你 苗路殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:34.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我是格里菲斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:36.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个鹰之团的团长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:40.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,多有失敬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:42.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我是苗路·沃夫拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:46.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是卢米阿斯领主巴拉格·沃夫拉姆的末子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:48.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在刚才的战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:50.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的臣下领民
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:54.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,从危机之中解救真的十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:59.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们才是要道谢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:04.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你们提供的粮草够我们支持几个月的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:07.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,您过奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:09.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:13.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在胸口不断涌动的强烈感情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:16.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,涌现出的 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:26.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,请您收下这把剑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:29.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:32.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:34.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对刚见面的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.15,0:21:37.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只说过一句话的这个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.61,0:21:39.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.29,0:21:42.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的内心深处这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:44.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格里菲斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:46.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:48.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,强而有力的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:53.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是 命运
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.63,0:23:29.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,出来了 伊斯多洛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.97,0:23:30.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.97,0:23:34.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法尔纳塞大人 请保证火不要熄灭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:35.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.85,0:23:37.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 卡思嘉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.89,0:23:39.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这么擅自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.44,0:23:42.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.15,0:23:46.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.49,0:23:48.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些土左卫门
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:42.36,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,就是 不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:46.30,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么解决啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:26.86,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,大家把柴火聚集起来 柴火要保持整夜不灭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.94,0:10:28.41,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么是你在指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.89,0:17:08.43,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,放开那女孩
Comment: 0,0:21:56.57,0:21:59.04,EDChs,,0,0,0,,/--------ED---------/
